Package: sherpa
Title: Carries your data between Shiny and Alpine.js
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person("Tobias", "Busch", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email="teebusch@gmail.com")
Description: Sherpa is a bridge between Shiny and Alpine.js. It mirrors Shiny reactiveValues in 
  an Alpine.js store in the browser and provides helpers for adding Alpine.js directives to 
  Shiny UI tags.
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()` or friends to pick a
    license
